In addition to these descriptions, the subtask should list all frontend code files and incorporate the original task's supplementary condition.
8) The composition should be kept as small as possible! (LESS THAN 3). If there are more than 3 tasks, consider merging the tasks and focus on the most essential features.
9) The workflow should not contain circles!

